        <span class="kv-k"><span class="es">Paso 1</span><span class="en">Step 1</span></span><span class="kv-v"><span class="es">Definir el variante (ej. K4 para a&ntilde;o calendario)</span><span class="en">Define the variant (e.g. K4 for calendar year)</span></span>
        <span class="kv-k"><span class="es">Paso 2</span><span class="en">Step 2</span></span><span class="kv-v"><span class="es">Definir los valores del variante (per&iacute;odos, fechas, campos)</span><span class="en">Define the variant values (periods, dates, fields)</span></span>
        <span class="kv-k"><span class="es">Paso 3</span><span class="en">Step 3</span></span><span class="kv-v"><span class="es">Asignar el variante al objeto relevante (c&oacute;digo de empresa, libro mayor)</span><span class="en">Assign the variant to the relevant object (company code, ledger)</span></span>
        <span class="kv-k"><span class="es">Se usa para</span><span class="en">Used for</span></span><span class="kv-v">Field Status Variant &middot; Posting Period Variant &middot; Fiscal Year Variant</span>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-blue" style="margin-top:10px">
        <span class="es"><strong>Beneficio clave:</strong> Si cambia una regla, se modifica solo el variante y el cambio aplica autom&aacute;ticamente a todos los c&oacute;digos de empresa asignados.</span>
        <span class="en"><strong>Key benefit:</strong> If a rule changes, only the variant is modified and the change applies automatically to all assigned company codes.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
