  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header" onclick="toggle(this)">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="ci ci-red">&#128197;</div><span class="es">Variantes de A&ntilde;o Fiscal (FYV)</span><span class="en">Fiscal Year Variants (FYV)</span></div>
      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="es">El FYV define los per&iacute;odos de publicaci&oacute;n. Hasta <strong>16 per&iacute;odos: 12 normales + 4 especiales</strong> (para asientos de cierre).</p>
      <p class="en">The FYV defines posting periods. Up to <strong>16 periods: 12 normal + 4 special</strong> (for closing entries).</p>
      <div class="two-col" style="margin-top:10px">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mt">Year-Independent</div>
          <p class="es">Mismas fechas todos los a&ntilde;os. Calendario (12 meses) o No-Calendario (fechas personalizadas, indicador -1/+1).</p>
          <p class="en">Same dates every year. Calendar (12 months) or Non-Calendar (custom dates, -1/+1 indicator).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mt">Year-Specific</div>
          <p class="es">Fechas diferentes entre a&ntilde;os. Incluye a&ntilde;os fiscales acortados (shortened fiscal year).</p>
          <p class="en">Different dates between years. Includes shortened fiscal years.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="alert alert-red" style="margin-top:10px">
        <strong>&#9888;&#65039; </strong>
        <span class="es">El FYV NO controla si un per&iacute;odo est&aacute; abierto o cerrado. Eso lo gestiona el <strong>Posting Period Variant</strong>. Son dos conceptos distintos.</span>
        <span class="en">The FYV does NOT control whether a period is open or closed. That is managed by the <strong>Posting Period Variant</strong>. These are two separate concepts.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
