    <div class="s-q">
      <span class="es">&#10067; Una empresa con 5 filiales quiere estados financieros seg&uacute;n IFRS (grupo) y GAAP local. &iquest;Qu&eacute; configuraci&oacute;n de libros mayores recomendar&iacute;as?</span>
      <span class="en">&#10067; A company with 5 subsidiaries wants financial statements per IFRS (group) and local GAAP. What ledger configuration would you recommend?</span>
