    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="alert alert-red">
        <strong><span class="es">REGLA ABSOLUTA</span><span class="en">ABSOLUTE RULE</span>: </strong>
        <span class="es">NUNCA se pueden hacer asientos directos en cuentas de reconciliaci&oacute;n. Solo a trav&eacute;s del subledger correspondiente.</span>
        <span class="en">NEVER make direct postings to reconciliation accounts. Only through the corresponding subledger.</span>
