        <tr><td>Park</td><td><span class="es">Guarda temporalmente SIN publicar. Editable. Puede publicarse despu&eacute;s.</span><span class="en">Saves temporarily WITHOUT posting. Editable. Can be posted later.</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Post</td><td><span class="es">Publicaci&oacute;n definitiva. Genera partidas en el Universal Journal.</span><span class="en">Definitive posting. Generates entries in the Universal Journal.</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Hold</td><td><span class="es">Solo visible para el usuario que lo retuvo.</span><span class="en">Only visible to the user who held it.</span></td></tr>
