      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="mini-card"><div class="mt">Entry View</div><p class="es">Partidas tal como las ingres&oacute; el usuario, sin dividir.</p><p class="en">Entries exactly as the user entered them, without splitting.</p></div>
        <div class="mini-card"><div class="mt">G/L View</div><p class="es">Partidas divididas seg&uacute;n las reglas de splitting activas.</p><p class="en">Entries split according to active splitting rules.</p></div>
      </div>
      <table style="margin-top:10px">
        <tr><th><span class="es">Tipo</span><span class="en">Type</span></th><th><span class="es">Descripci&oacute;n</span><span class="en">Description</span></th></tr>
        <tr><td>Passive</td><td><span class="es">Durante la compensaci&oacute;n: las caracter&iacute;sticas del documento compensado se copian en la misma proporci&oacute;n.</span><span class="en">During clearing: the characteristics of the cleared document are copied in the same proportion.</span></td></tr>
