  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header" onclick="toggle(this)">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="ci ci-red">&#128260;</div><span class="es">Transacciones entre C&oacute;digos de Empresa (Cross-Company)</span><span class="en">Cross-Company Code Transactions</span></div>
      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="alert alert-red">
        <strong><span class="es">F&oacute;rmula cuentas de compensaci&oacute;n</span><span class="en">Clearing accounts formula</span>: </strong>N &times; (N-1).
        <span class="es"> Ejemplo: 3 c&oacute;digos &rarr; 3&times;2 = <strong>6 cuentas de compensaci&oacute;n</strong>.</span>
        <span class="en"> Example: 3 codes &rarr; 3&times;2 = <strong>6 clearing accounts</strong>.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="kv" style="margin-top:10px">
        <span class="kv-k"><span class="es">Documento</span><span class="en">Document</span></span><span class="kv-v"><span class="es">Un documento separado por Company Code, vinculados por n&uacute;mero de documento entre c&oacute;digos.</span><span class="en">One separate document per Company Code, linked by the cross-company document number.</span></span>
        <span class="kv-k"><span class="es">Impuesto</span><span class="en">Tax</span></span><span class="kv-v"><span class="es">Siempre al c&oacute;digo del PRIMER &iacute;tem. Ingresar SIEMPRE el &iacute;tem de factura primero.</span><span class="en">Always to the FIRST item's code. ALWAYS enter the invoice item first.</span></span>
