      <h2><span class="es">Compensaci&oacute;n de Documentos Financieros</span><span class="en">Financial Document Clearing</span></h2>
      <p><span class="es">Partidas Abiertas &middot; 3 M&eacute;todos &middot; Pagos &middot; Diferencias &middot; Reason Codes &middot; Tipo de Cambio</span><span class="en">Open Items &middot; 3 Methods &middot; Payments &middot; Differences &middot; Reason Codes &middot; Exchange Rate</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="exam-tip">
    <div class="label">&#128204; <span class="es">Claves del Examen</span><span class="en">Exam Keys</span></div>
    <p class="es">Partial: factura e importe siguen abiertos. Residual: los originales se compensan, queda solo el nuevo residual. Dentro de tolerancias &rarr; ajuste autom&aacute;tico.</p>
    <p class="en">Partial: invoice and amount remain open. Residual: originals are cleared, only the new residual remains. Within tolerances &rarr; automatic adjustment.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card open">
    <div class="card-header" onclick="toggle(this)">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="ci ci-blue">&#9989;</div><span class="es">Los 3 M&eacute;todos de Compensaci&oacute;n</span><span class="en">The 3 Clearing Methods</span></div>
      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <table>
        <tr><th><span class="es">M&eacute;todo</span><span class="en">Method</span></th><th><span class="es">Descripci&oacute;n y uso</span><span class="en">Description and use</span></th></tr>
        <tr><td>Post with Clearing</td><td><span class="es">Se ingresa el importe y se seleccionan las partidas abiertas manualmente. Se crea un documento de compensaci&oacute;n. Base del proceso de pagos manual.</span><span class="en">Enter the amount and manually select open items. A clearing document is created. Base of the manual payment process.</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Account Clearing</td><td><span class="es">El sistema cierra partidas que tienen saldo cero entre ellas. Sin pago nuevo. Usable en cualquier cuenta con OIM activo.</span><span class="en">System closes items that have zero balance against each other. No new payment. Usable on any account with active OIM.</span></td></tr>
        <tr><td>Automatic Clearing</td><td><span class="es">Agrupa partidas por CoCd, tipo de cuenta, cuenta, moneda. Si el saldo en moneda local es cero &rarr; compensaci&oacute;n autom&aacute;tica.</span><span class="en">Groups items by CoCd, account type, account, currency. If local currency balance is zero &rarr; automatic clearing.</span></td></tr>
      </table>
      <div class="alert alert-amber" style="margin-top:10px">
        <span class="es"><strong>El programa autom&aacute;tico NO compensa:</strong> Noted items &middot; Publicaciones estad&iacute;sticas &middot; Anticipos con diferencia &middot; Retenci&oacute;n de impuestos.</span>
        <span class="en"><strong>The automatic program does NOT clear:</strong> Noted items &middot; Statistical postings &middot; Down payments with difference &middot; Tax withholding.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header" onclick="toggle(this)">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="ci ci-amber">&#128201;</div><span class="es">Diferencias de Pago: Partial vs. Residual</span><span class="en">Payment Differences: Partial vs. Residual</span></div>
      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mt">Partial Payment</div>
          <p class="es"><strong>Factura original + pago parcial quedan ABIERTOS.</strong> El pago se referencia a la factura pero no la cierra.</p>
          <p class="en"><strong>Original invoice + partial payment remain OPEN.</strong> The payment is referenced to the invoice but does not close it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mt">Residual Item &#11088;</div>
          <p class="es">La factura original y el pago se <strong>COMPENSAN</strong>. SAP crea una nueva partida abierta por la diferencia.</p>
          <p class="en">The original invoice and payment are <strong>CLEARED</strong>. SAP creates a new open item for the difference.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="sub">
        <div class="sub-title">Reason Codes</div>
        <ul class="lst">
          <li class="es"><span class="es">Describen la causa de la diferencia</span></li>
          <li class="en"><span class="en">Describe the cause of the difference</span></li>
          <li class="es"><span class="es">Controlan el tipo de aviso de pago al cliente (dunning)</span></li>
          <li class="en"><span class="en">Control the type of payment notice to the customer (dunning)</span></li>
          <li class="es"><span class="es">Determinan la cuenta G/L de publicaci&oacute;n de la partida residual</span></li>
          <li class="en"><span class="en">Determine the G/L account for posting the residual item</span></li>
          <li class="es"><span class="es">Excluyen partidas residuales en disputa de verificaciones de l&iacute;mite de cr&eacute;dito</span></li>
          <li class="en"><span class="en">Exclude disputed residual items from credit limit checks</span></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-header" onclick="toggle(this)">
      <div class="card-title"><div class="ci ci-green">&#128184;</div><span class="es">Proceso de Pago Manual</span><span class="en">Manual Payment Process</span></div>
      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <div class="two-col">
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mt">Incoming Payment (AR)</div>
          <p class="es">Compensa un importe de d&eacute;bito abierto (factura de cliente). Cargos bancarios se SUMAN al importe del pago.</p>
          <p class="en">Clears an open debit amount (customer invoice). Bank charges are ADDED to the payment amount.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mini-card">
          <div class="mt">Outgoing Payment (AP)</div>
          <p class="es">Compensa un importe de cr&eacute;dito abierto (factura de proveedor). Cargos bancarios se RESTAN del importe del pago.</p>
          <p class="en">Clears an open credit amount (vendor invoice). Bank charges are SUBTRACTED from the payment amount.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="scenario">
    <div class="s-label">&#128293; <span class="es">Escenario de Examen 2026</span><span class="en">2026 Exam Scenario</span></div>
    <div class="s-q">
      <span class="es">&#10067; Una empresa recibe EUR 9.850 contra una factura de EUR 10.000. La diferencia de EUR 150 est&aacute; dentro de la tolerancia. &iquest;Qu&eacute; hace SAP?</span>
      <span class="en">&#10067; A company receives EUR 9,850 against an invoice of EUR 10,000. The EUR 150 difference is within tolerance. What does SAP do?</span>
    </div>
    <div class="s-a">
      <span class="es"><strong>Respuesta experta:</strong> SAP verifica que EUR 150 est&aacute; dentro de los l&iacute;mites del <strong>grupo de tolerancia del BP</strong> y del <strong>grupo de tolerancia G/L</strong>. Si ambas tolerancias lo permiten, SAP publica autom&aacute;ticamente los EUR 150 como ajuste o cancelaci&oacute;n en la cuenta predefinida, y <strong>compensa la factura en su totalidad</strong>. No se requiere intervenci&oacute;n manual.</span>
      <span class="en"><strong>Expert answer:</strong> SAP verifies that EUR 150 is within the limits of the <strong>BP tolerance group</strong> and the <strong>G/L tolerance group</strong>. If both tolerances allow it, SAP automatically posts the EUR 150 as a write-off to the predefined account, and <strong>clears the invoice in full</strong>. No manual intervention required.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

