      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-body"><span class="step-path">Ledgers &rarr; Ledger &rarr; Deactivate a Ledger for a Company Code</span><span class="es">Introducir 2L &rarr; verificar que GR## est&aacute; sin restricciones de a&ntilde;o (ledger activo para todos los ejercicios).</span><span class="en">Enter 2L &rarr; verify GR## has no year restrictions (ledger active for all fiscal years).</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ex-card" data-unit="u2">
    <div class="ex-header" onclick="toggleEx(this)">
      <span class="ex-num">EJ 6</span>
      <div><div class="ex-title"><span class="es">Create and Maintain Fiscal Year Variants</span><span class="en">Create and Maintain Fiscal Year Variants</span></div><div class="ex-sub"><span class="es">Calendar year &middot; Non-calendar FYV &middot; Restricci&oacute;n CO Area</span><span class="en">Calendar year &middot; Non-calendar FYV &middot; CO Area restriction</span></div></div>
      <span class="chevron">&#8250;</span>
    </div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">1</div><div class="step-body"><span class="step-path">FA Global Settings &rarr; Ledgers &rarr; Fiscal Year and Posting Periods &rarr; Maintain Fiscal Year Variant</span><span class="es">New Entries: FV=##+30 | Calendar yr=Selected | 12 posting periods | 4 special periods.</span><span class="en">New Entries: FV=##+30 | Calendar yr=Selected | 12 posting periods | 4 special periods.</span></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">2</div><div class="step-body"><span class="es">Intentar asignar al CoCd &rarr; aparece aviso CA A000 &rarr; elegir NO &rarr; <strong>CANCELAR sin guardar</strong>.</span><span class="en">Try to assign to CoCd &rarr; CA A000 warning appears &rarr; choose NO &rarr; <strong>CANCEL without saving</strong>.</span></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">3</div><div class="step-body"><span class="es">Crear FYV no-calendario (##+60) &mdash; Abr&ndash;Mar: 4 per&iacute;odos + 1 especial.</span><span class="en">Create non-calendar FYV (##+60) &mdash; Apr&ndash;Mar: 4 periods + 1 special.</span><span class="step-path">Month 03/Day 31/Period 4/Year Shift -1 | 06/30/1/0 | 09/30/2/0 | 12/31/3/0</span></div></div>
      <div class="alert alert-red" style="margin-top:10px"><strong>&#9888;&#65039; </strong><span class="es">NO se puede cambiar el FYV de un CoCd de forma independiente si est&aacute; asignado a un Controlling Area. Afecta a TODOS los CoCd del CA.</span><span class="en">The FYV of a CoCd CANNOT be changed independently if assigned to a Controlling Area. It affects ALL CoCd in the CA.</span></div>
