      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">12</div><div class="step-body"><span class="step-path">FA Global Settings &rarr; Document &rarr; Document Types &rarr; Define Document Types</span><span class="es">New: Doc Type=ZD## | Number Range=## | Account Types=D+S.</span><span class="en">New: Doc Type=ZD## | Number Range=## | Account Types=D+S.</span></div></div>
