      <div class="alert alert-red" style="margin-top:10px"><strong>&#9888;&#65039;</strong> <span class="es">Si el Doc Type NO est&aacute; clasificado y el splitting est&aacute; activo, no se puede postear.</span><span class="en">If the Doc Type is NOT classified and splitting is active, posting is not possible.</span></div>
