  <div class="ex-card" data-unit="u4"><div class="ex-header" onclick="toggleEx(this)"><span class="ex-num">EJ 14-15</span><div><div class="ex-title"><span class="es">Field Status Group, Posting Period Variant</span><span class="en">Field Status Group, Posting Period Variant</span></div><div class="ex-sub">FS## &middot; PP## &middot; OB52</div></div><span class="chevron">&#8250;</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">14</div><div class="step-body"><span class="step-path">FA Global Settings &rarr; Ledgers &rarr; Fields &rarr; Define Field Status Variants</span><span class="es">FSV 0010 &rarr; New FSG FS## &rarr; configurar campos. Asignar FSG a cuenta GL en Manage G/L Account Master Data.</span><span class="en">FSV 0010 &rarr; New FSG FS## &rarr; configure fields. Assign FSG to GL account in Manage G/L Account Master Data.</span></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">15</div><div class="step-body"><span class="step-path">FA Global Settings &rarr; Ledgers &rarr; Fiscal Year &rarr; Posting Periods &rarr; Define Variants / Open and Close / Assign Variants</span><span class="es">Crear variante PP## &rarr; abrir per&iacute;odos (tipo &lsquo;+&rsquo; primero) &rarr; asignar a CoCd GR##.</span><span class="en">Create variant PP## &rarr; open periods (type &lsquo;+&rsquo; first) &rarr; assign to CoCd GR##.</span></div></div>
