  <div class="ex-card" data-unit="u4"><div class="ex-header" onclick="toggleEx(this)"><span class="ex-num">EJ 16-17</span><div><div class="ex-title"><span class="es">Tolerance Group &amp; Post FI Documents</span><span class="en">Tolerance Group &amp; Post FI Documents</span></div><div class="ex-sub"><span class="es">Park &middot; Post &middot; Simular</span><span class="en">Park &middot; Post &middot; Simulate</span></div></div><span class="chevron">&#8250;</span></div>
    <div class="ex-body">
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">16</div><div class="step-body"><span class="step-path">FA Global Settings &rarr; Document &rarr; Tolerance Groups &rarr; Define Tolerance Groups for Employees</span><span class="es">New: CoCd=GR## | Group=## | l&iacute;mites de importe &rarr; asignar a usuario S4F12-##.</span><span class="en">New: CoCd=GR## | Group=## | amount limits &rarr; assign to user S4F12-##.</span></div></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="step-num">17</div><div class="step-body"><span class="es">Fiori Post General Journal Entries &rarr; Check (simular) &rarr; Park (aparcar) o Post (publicar definitivo).</span><span class="en">Fiori Post General Journal Entries &rarr; Check (simulate) &rarr; Park (temporary) or Post (definitive).</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

